{"tid":366782,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"去歐洲出疹，成個月都唔好，點算？","createTime":"2017-08-20T09:29:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T12:49:43.000Z","uid":113113,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b6fc9ffc4cbb6a97b002d0be38d86f80d1a9c6f7","tid":366782,"uid":113113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T09:29:48.000Z","msg":"上個月去歐洲，中途就出咗疹，開始似蚊咬，然後變成一個個有粉紅色邊但中間係肉色嘅印。<br />\n開頭生係手臂，後來大腿，pat pat ，然後最近背都有啲&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n而且腹瀉咗兩星期啦！<br />\n果陣以為敏感，又無發燒，但就有啲作嘔咁。<br />\n睇咗4個醫生，一個話敏感，一個話病毒感染，一個話牛皮癬，一個話濕疹，但全部都醫我唔好！！！<br />\n到底係咩事？<br />\n已經洗咗幾千蚊，中西醫專科都睇曬！！！<br />\n求連登神醫解救！！！"},{"pid":"7fecef780d778cbd380c327f373df702dabce508","tid":366782,"uid":101555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T09:31:32.000Z","msg":"有無做blood test"},{"pid":"a257323733fe8c501932594112719e5294ee4df2","tid":366782,"uid":31261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T09:32:18.000Z","msg":"相呢"},{"pid":"3775a229c455e69a5b08f1d5bc0df780e6b691e6","tid":366782,"uid":113113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T09:36:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無做blood test</blockquote><br />\n無啊，係test 啲咩？可以邊到做？"},{"pid":"83fa923e850bb182c72e3f10d6cce48269ba0118","tid":366782,"uid":113113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T09:38:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>相呢</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/9mb1ps20\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F9mb1ps20&h=f23ebe6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n類固醇都搽埋&hellip;"},{"pid":"8d90cf4f12e9316a6936155c56411edbe4ce6ec2","tid":366782,"uid":113113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T09:56:39.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"73ac155d7f6587a2b5df03cb2ee9999ae31d48e4","tid":366782,"uid":113113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T09:56:56.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"8bd56fcfd52d564da14fccac4a257c25503e8229","tid":366782,"uid":113113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T10:15:44.000Z","msg":"求救 我之前都無出過呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65fa0472c5f77603ec0c0c82ab06c979d21178cc","tid":366782,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T10:32:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無做blood test</blockquote><br />\n無啊，係test 啲咩？可以邊到做？</blockquote><br />\n好似係test 有冇病毒感染，如果有就可能係病毒疹，不過就算知道係都冇用，可能醫生都係不斷開抗生素試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我諗可能休息對你最緊要，因為其實好多嘢都會令你出疹，好可能好返都未知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e290deeeaf3cf22afc8ba27376499badf374def3","tid":366782,"uid":113113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T11:56:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無做blood test</blockquote><br />\n無啊，係test 啲咩？可以邊到做？</blockquote><br />\n好似係test 有冇病毒感染，如果有就可能係病毒疹，不過就算知道係都冇用，可能醫生都係不斷開抗生素試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我諗可能休息對你最緊要，因為其實好多嘢都會令你出疹，好可能好返都未知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n由出疹到而家已經成個半月&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似唔覺會好返咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af12274b4acfbd5ed938b68bf55d5c7fed18d6e1","tid":366782,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T12:01:01.000Z","msg":"睇醫生啦屌"},{"pid":"23f376726144b11173abd0bfcb3f3bb18584c085","tid":366782,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T12:01:57.000Z","msg":"個款似病毒感染"},{"pid":"e59a04dcaa0dc321a1aeb3788573b913358a9178","tid":366782,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T12:02:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無做blood test</blockquote><br />\n無啊，係test 啲咩？可以邊到做？</blockquote><br />\n好似係test 有冇病毒感染，如果有就可能係病毒疹，不過就算知道係都冇用，可能醫生都係不斷開抗生素試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我諗可能休息對你最緊要，因為其實好多嘢都會令你出疹，好可能好返都未知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n病毒開抗生素梗係冇用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5a1383cf9a7647ec832e8c8b015dee5e90bfcbe","tid":366782,"uid":113113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T13:46:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇醫生啦屌</blockquote><br />\n睇咗5次4個醫生，西醫中醫皮膚專科都睇埋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba7dd8eb3dc070bf25c3e3c0509a59a52531643e","tid":366782,"uid":113113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T13:46:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n病毒開抗生素梗係冇用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n話我病毒感染果個都係出抗生素&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b5128b1dc3486aac60565e83224bcb370b7dda0","tid":366782,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T14:13:39.000Z","msg":"似蕁痲疹過敏<br />\n有冇食過乜剌激野？<br />\n會唔會退完返發？<br />\n有冇特定時間出？<br />\n飲水習慣有冇變？"},{"pid":"17579db9d6c69182ede3a3b32da8459cc4204abb","tid":366782,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T15:18:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e15b5c66a91df29821c2d2d337db8bf264590d4","tid":366782,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T15:31:36.000Z","msg":"可能對奶敏感，亞洲人常見"},{"pid":"9e521da299b7ba4032c1187d2d356ee14bba0156","tid":366782,"uid":65905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T15:46:50.000Z","msg":"喂認真 我都岩岩去完歐洲<br />\n我都有好似你咁瘋狂出疹<br />\n手臀同小腿 出到我完全瞓唔到<br />\n頂左兩個禮拜終於返到香港睇醫生 但係依然唔知咩原因<br />\n開左抗生素同類固醇藥膏比我<br />\n同埋建議我去做食物敏感測試（不過食物敏感應該發到全身都係 唔會係局部）<br />\n<br />\n我自己就覺得係因為我有一晚搭過夜巴士 個晚無沖涼<br />\n可能惹到污糟野<br />\n咁岩我之後個幾日都喺啲勁熱嘅地方（近四十度）<br />\nkeep住不停出汗 所以出熱痱/引發到出呢啲疹<br />\n<br />\n但呢層都只係我自己猜測 <br />\n因為本身我身體麻麻地 成日都因為免疫力差而病<br />\n喺香港嘅時候有時候空氣差都會皮膚過敏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"352b0863f42d10521bb94f9f5bc1b957e4a452db","tid":366782,"uid":113113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T16:15:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>似蕁痲疹過敏<br />\n有冇食過乜剌激野？<br />\n會唔會退完返發？<br />\n有冇特定時間出？<br />\n飲水習慣有冇變？</blockquote><br />\n無咩特別，啲嘢我平時都有食咖&hellip;&hellip;不過酒就有次飲完嘔，我本身就酒敏感。<br />\n但係飲之前都其實出咗，開頭幾粒，然後愈來愈多&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n睇完醫生都有退，但啱啱又好似多返，可能係我轉咗第二隻藥膏？"},{"pid":"5bb29041efa4343742c3ef0363e19ceb3a94189b","tid":366782,"uid":113113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T16:21:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>喂認真 我都岩岩去完歐洲<br />\n我都有好似你咁瘋狂出疹<br />\n手臀同小腿 出到我完全瞓唔到<br />\n頂左兩個禮拜終於返到香港睇醫生 但係依然唔知咩原因<br />\n開左抗生素同類固醇藥膏比我<br />\n同埋建議我去做食物敏感測試（不過食物敏感應該發到全身都係 唔會係局部）<br />\n<br />\n我自己就覺得係因為我有一晚搭過夜巴士 個晚無沖涼<br />\n可能惹到污糟野<br />\n咁岩我之後個幾日都喺啲勁熱嘅地方（近四十度）<br />\nkeep住不停出汗 所以出熱痱/引發到出呢啲<br />\n<br />\n疹<br />\n<br />\n但呢層都只係我自己猜測 <br />\n因為本身我身體麻麻地 成日都因為免疫力差而病<br />\n喺香港嘅時候有時候空氣差都會皮膚過敏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係！我都有去熱嘅地方日日曬！同埋身體都差！<br />\n我果陣以為光敏感或曬傷，但返到hk 都成個月，都重係有，所以應該唔係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我果陣有日日沖涼&hellip;&hellip;真係唔明&hellip;&hellip;可能床有菌？<br />\n咁你而家好返未？如果呢到沉咗可以tg 我: <br />\n@AragakiYuiBB<br />\n<br />\n其實任何人可以救到我都可以tg 我！！！無限感激！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fd21a9b2587c4abce45fec6ec20c796a0639a5b","tid":366782,"uid":113113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T16:24:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>喂認真 我都岩岩去完歐洲<br />\n我都有好似你咁瘋狂出疹<br />\n手臀同小腿 出到我完全瞓唔到<br />\n頂左兩個禮拜終於返到香港睇醫生 但係依然唔知咩原因<br />\n開左抗生素同類固醇藥膏比我<br />\n同埋建議我去做食物敏感測試（不過食物敏感應該發到全身都係 唔會係局部）<br />\n<br />\n我自己就覺得係因為我有一晚搭過夜巴士 個晚無沖涼<br />\n可能惹到污糟野<br />\n咁岩我之後個幾日都喺啲勁熱嘅地方（近四十度）<br />\nkeep住不停出汗 所以出熱痱/引發到出呢啲疹<br />\n<br />\n但呢層都只係我自己猜測<br />\n因為本身我身體麻麻地 成日都因為免疫力差而病<br />\n喺香港嘅時候有時候空氣差都會皮膚過敏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係你係會痕？我唔痕咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做咩測試又好似好貴，我呢幾日都戒蛋奶牛蝦都係咁&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n咁你有無test 到？"},{"pid":"ec403abc79fdd8071d614b128a964154f3ede609","tid":366782,"uid":79182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T16:25:58.000Z","msg":"我個陣都係歐洲搞左好耐都唔好<br />\nR到流血 食左藥搽左藥膏都唔好<br />\n但返到香港無理佢就好左"},{"pid":"83173115b2bdf6471acb12f2668b78cb124506cf","tid":366782,"uid":79182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T16:27:30.000Z","msg":"認真忍下手唔好R<br />\n我成隻手臂都仲係印<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/21/002726_2f8b77f86a07c3c644a5c49aef06cf5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F21%2F002726_2f8b77f86a07c3c644a5c49aef06cf5a.jpg&h=0111af8d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e99dcf3836b2d2db1d46ba2d95c753675d879077","tid":366782,"uid":113113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T16:37:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真忍下手唔好R<br />\n我成隻手臂都仲係印<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/21/002726_2f8b77f86a07c3c644a5c49aef06cf5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F21%2F002726_2f8b77f86a07c3c644a5c49aef06cf5a.jpg&h=0111af8d&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我無R, 因為真係唔痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}